# Web3Forms access key — powers the contact form (https://web3forms.com, free).
# 1. Go to web3forms.com, enter info@lulula.nl (or her Gmail) as the destination.
# 2. Copy the access key they email you into a real .env.local file:
#      NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-real-key-here
# The NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix inlines it at build time (fine — Web3Forms keys are public by design;
# spam is handled by their honeypot + domain settings, not by hiding the key).
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=replace-me-with-web3forms-access-key
